Dependencies
============

build-essential
libgcrypt11-dev
libssl-dev (Openssl)
libboost-serialization-dev
libboost-dev

Installation
========

Getting the source via subversion:
----------------------------------
svn co http://anytun.org/svn/anytun/

Building from source
--------------------
cd anytun
./configure
cd Sockets
make
cd ..
make
